Derived from EhBASIC
====================

The BASIC interpreter in this project -- "MFC BASIC" (src/kernel/basic.asm,
built into basic.rom) -- is Derived from EhBASIC (Enhanced BASIC) by Lee
Davison. This work started from EhBASIC version 2.22p5.

This NOTICE, and the "Derived from EhBASIC" string embedded in the BASIC
sign-on banner, are provided to satisfy the EhBASIC distribution terms below.


